# Each seed: instruction, output, category
SEED_LIBRARY: List[Dict[str, str]] = [
    # ── Обща медицина (General Medicine) ──
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на тип 2 диабет?", "output": "Тип 2 диабетът се проявява с жажда, често уриниране, умора, замъглено зрение и бавно заздравяване на рани. В България скринингът се извършва чрез кръвна проба за глюкоза на гладно или HbA1c. НЗОК покрива метформин (Glucophage) като първа линия терапия. Препоръчва се консултация с ендокринолог.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува хипертония в България?", "output": "Хипертонията се лекува с промяна на начина на живот и антихипертензивни медикаменти. НЗОК покрива ACE инхибитори (Enalapril, Perindopril), ARB (Losartan), калциеви антагонисти (Amlodipine) и диуретици. Целевото АД е под 140/90 mmHg. Регулярни контроли при личен лекар са задължителни.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е метаболитен синдром?", "output": "Метаболитният синдром включва коремно затлъстяване, повишена кръвна захар, хипертония и дислипидемия. В България засяга над 25% от възрастните. Лечението включва диета, физическа активност и медикаменти при нужда. НЗОК покрива статини и антидиабетни средства.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са признаците на инфекция на горните дихателни пътища?", "output": "ГРИП и настинка включват кашлица, хрема, болка в гърлото, температура и мускулни болки. В България сезонът е от октомври до март. Симптоматично лечение с парацетамол (Efferalgan), ibuprofen и обилни течности. Антибиотици не са показани при вирусни инфекции.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е затлъстяване и как се диагностицира?", "output": "Затлъстяването се дефинира с BMI ≥ 30 kg/m². В България 23% от възрастните са с затлъстяване. Диагностиката включва BMI, обиколка на талията и оценка на съпътстващи заболявания. НЗОК може да покрие Orlistat при BMI ≥ 30 с комorbidities след 3 месеца диета.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви вaccини са задължителни за възрастни в България?", "output": "Задължителни вaccини за възрастни включват реваксинация срещу дифтерия и tetanus на 10 години, сезонен грипен вaccин (препоръчителен за рискови групи) и COVID-19 вaccин. НЗОК покрива грипната вaccина за възрастни над 65 години и хронично болни.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е анемия и как се лекува?", "output": "Анемията е намален хемoglobin. Най-честата форма е желязодефицитна анемия. Диагностика: пълна кръвна картина, феритин, серумно желязо. Лечение: Ferrograd (желязо), диета богата на желязо. НЗОК покрива Ferrograd при доказан дефицит.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на хипothyreoidism?", "output": "Хипothyreoidismът причинява умора, натрупване на тегло, студен intolerance, запек и депресия. Диагностика: TSH, FT4. Лечение: Levothyroxine (Euthyrox, L-Thyroxine) — покрит от НЗОК. Контрол на TSH на 6-8 седмици след промяна на дозата.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е ГERB и как се лекува?", "output": "Гастроesophagealната reflux болест (ГERB) причинява киселини, регurgitaция и болка в гърдите. Лечение: Omeprazole (Omeprotec), Esomeprazole (Nexium) — покрити от НЗОК. Промяна на диета: избягване на пикantна храна, алкохол, late night eating.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са рисковете от затлъстяване при деца?", "output": "Детското затлъстяване води до тип 2 диабет, хипертония и сърдечно-съдови заболявания. В България 20% от децата са с наднормено тегло. Преvention: здравословна диета, ограничаване на захар и физическа активност минимум 60 мин/ден.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира и лекува подагра?", "output": "Подagрата е артрит от uric acid crystals. Симптоми: остра болка в стъпалото, подобна на big toe. Диагностика: uric acid, joint fluid. Лечение: Colchicine, Allopurinol (Zyloric) — покрити от НЗОК. Диета: ограничаване на месо, алкохол, fructose.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е COPD и как се управлява?", "output": "COPD (хронична обструктивна белодробна болест) е прогресиращо белодробно заболяване от тютюнопушене. Лечение: Bronchodilators (Salbutamol, Tiotropium), inhaled corticosteroids. НЗОК покрива Symbicort, Spiriva. Спиране на тютюнопушенето е ключово.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на хепatitis B?", "output": "Hepatitis B може да бъде асymptomatic или да причини жълтеница, умора, abdominal pain. Вaccинацията срещу HBV е задължителна в българския календар. Диагностика: HBsAg, anti-HBc. Лечение при хроничен HBV: Tenofovir, Entecavir — покрити от НЗОК.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е osteoporosis и как се предотвратява?", "output": "Osteoporosisът е намалена костна плътност с риск от фрактури. В Българia жените след menopause са високорискови. Преvention: калций, витамин D, упражнения. Лечение: Bisphosphonates (Alendronate) — покрити от НЗОК. DEXA scan за диагностика.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува алергичен rhinit?", "output": "Алергичният rhinit причинява кихане, хрема и сърбеж в очите. В България polen сезонът е пролет-есен. Лечение: Antihistamines (Cetirizine, Loratadine), nasal corticosteroids (Fluticasone). НЗОК покрива Cetirizine и Loratadine.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е sleep apnea?", "output": "Obstructive sleep apnea причинява хъркане, apnea episodes и дневна сънливост. Рискови фактори: затлъстяване, мъжки пол. Диагностика: polysomnography. Лечение: CPAP терапия, weight loss. Направление от pneumolog в България.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на urинарна инфекция?", "output": "UTI причинява burning при urination, често urination, pelvic pain. Диагностика: urinalysis, urine culture. Лечение: Antibiotics (Nitrofurantoin, Ciprofloxacin) — покрити от НЗОК. Обилни течности и cranberry може да помогнат.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е fibromyalgia?", "output": "Fibromyalgia е хронично заболяване с diffused muscle pain, fatigue и sleep problems. Диагностика: clinical criteria. Лечение: Pregabalin (Lyrica), Duloxetine — частично покрити от НЗОК. Multidisciplinary approach: физioterapia, cognitive behavioral therapy.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява asthma?", "output": "Asthma е хронично възпаление на bronchi с wheezing и dyspnea. Лечение: Inhaled corticosteroids (Budesonide), bronchodilators (Salbutamol). НЗОК покрива Symbicort, Ventolin. Asthma action plan от pneumolog.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е celiac disease?", "output": "Celiac disease е autoimmune реакция на gluten. Симптоми: diarrhea, bloating, weight loss. Диагностика: anti-tTG antibodies, duodenal biopsy. Лечение: strict gluten-free diet. НЗОК не покрива специални храни, но диагностиката е безплатна.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на influenza?", "output": "Influenza причинява high fever, muscle aches, headache, cough. В България сезонът е декември-февруари. Лечение: rest, fluids, Oseltamivir (Tamiflu) при early presentation. НЗОК покрива Tamiflu при рискови пациенти.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира Lyme disease?", "output": "Lyme disease от tick bites причинява erythema migrans, fever, joint pain. В България ticks са common в горски зони. Лечение: Doxycycline 14-21 days — покрит от НЗОК. Prevention: repellents, проверка след престой на открито.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е GERD при бременни?", "output": "ГERB е common при бременност от progesterone effects. Лечение: dietary changes, Antacids (Rennie), Omeprazole при severe symptoms — безопасен в pregnancy. Консултация с gynecologist.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на vitamin D deficiency?", "output": "Vitamin D deficiency причинява bone pain, muscle weakness, fatigue. В България prevalence е висока през зимата. Диагностика: 25-OH vitamin D. Лечение: Cholecalciferol (Vigantol) — покрит от НЗОК при дефицит.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува eczema?", "output": "Atopic eczema причинява itchy, red skin patches. Лечение: Emollients, topical corticosteroids (Hydrocortisone), Tacrolimus. НЗОК покрива базови emollients и corticosteroids. Avoid triggers: stress, allergens.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е metabolic acidosis?", "output": "Metabolic acidosis е low blood pH от various causes including DKA, kidney failure. Симптоми: deep breathing, confusion, nausea. Emergency treatment required. DKA management: insulin, fluids, electrolyte correction in hospital.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на hyperthyroidism?", "output": "Hyperthyroidism причинява weight loss, palpitations, heat intolerance, tremor. Диагностика: low TSH, high FT4. Лечение: Methimazole (Thiamazole), radioiodine, surgery. НЗОК покрива Thiamazole.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява chronic kidney disease?", "output": "CKD се staging по eGFR. Управление: blood pressure control (ACE inhibitors), diabetes management, dietary protein restriction. НЗОК покрива dialysis при stage 5. Nephrolog referral при eGFR < 60.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е psoriasis?", "output": "Psoriasis е autoimmune skin disease с red scaly plaques. Лечение: Topical corticosteroids, Vitamin D analogs, Methotrexate при severe. НЗОК покрива Calcipotriol, Methotrexate. Dermatolog referral.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на meningitis?", "output": "Meningitis причинява severe headache, neck stiffness, fever, photophobia. EMERGENCY — незабавно обаждане на 112. Вaccinaция срещу meningococcus е в българския календар. Treatment: IV antibiotics in hospital.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    # ── Кардиология (Cardiology) ──
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на сърдечна недостатъчност?", "output": "Сърдечната недостатъчност причинява dyspnea, fatigue, peripheral edema, orthopnea. В България CVD е leading cause of death. Лечение: ACE inhibitors, Beta-blockers (Bisoprolol), Diuretics (Furosemide) — всички покрити от НЗОК. Cardiolog referral.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е остър myocardial infarction?", "output": "AMI (infarct) е blockage на coronary artery с chest pain, dyspnea, diaphoresis. EMERGENCY — 112 незабавно. В България PCI centers в Sofia, Plovdiv, Varna. Treatment: aspirin, clopidogrel, statins, reperfusion therapy.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са видовете arrhythmia?", "output": "Arrhythmias включват atrial fibrillation, ventricular tachycardia, bradycardia. AF е most common — risk of stroke. Лечение: Anticoagulants (Warfarin, Rivaroxaban), rate control (Bisoprolol). НЗОК покрива NOACs при AF с CHA2DS2-VASc ≥ 2.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира hypertension?", "output": "Hypertension: BP ≥ 140/90 mmHg на multiple occasions. Ambulatory BP monitoring се препоръчва. В България home BP monitoring е encouraged. Treatment per ESC guidelines adapted locally.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е angina pectoris?", "output": "Stable angina е chest pain от coronary artery disease при exertion. Лечение: Nitrates (Nitroglycerin), Beta-blockers, statins. НЗОК покрива Isosorbide mononitrate. Cardiac stress test за diagnosis.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са risk factors за CVD в България?", "output": "Risk factors: smoking (33% мъже), hypertension, diabetes, dyslipidemia, obesity, sedentary lifestyle. Bulgarian CVD mortality е among highest in EU. Prevention: smoking cessation, Mediterranean diet, exercise.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува atrial fibrillation?", "output": "AF management: rate/rhythm control, stroke prevention. Anticoagulation: Apixaban (Eliquis), Rivaroxaban (Xarelto) — покрити от НЗОК. Cardioversion при symptomatic patients. CHA2DS2-VASc score guides anticoagulation.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е heart valve disease?", "output": "Valve disease: stenosis или regurgitation на aortic/mitral valves. Симптоми: dyspnea, syncope, chest pain. Diagnosis: echocardiography. Severe cases: valve replacement — покрито от НЗОК в approved centers.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на pericarditis?", "output": "Pericarditis причинява sharp chest pain worse with breathing, fever. Diagnosis: ECG, echocardiography. Treatment: NSAIDs (Ibuprofen), Colchicine. Most cases resolve. Cardiolog follow-up.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява dyslipidemia?", "output": "High cholesterol increases CVD risk. Target LDL < 1.8 mmol/L при high risk. Treatment: Statins (Atorvastatin, Rosuvastatin) — покрити от НЗОК. Lifestyle: diet, exercise. Lipid panel annually.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е cardiomyopathy?", "output": "Cardiomyopathy е weakened heart muscle. Types: dilated, hypertrophic, restrictive. Симптоми: heart failure symptoms. Diagnosis: echocardiography, MRI. Treatment: heart failure medications, ICD при risk.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на pulmonary embolism?", "output": "PE причинява sudden dyspnea, chest pain, tachycardia. EMERGENCY — 112. Risk factors: immobilization, surgery, cancer. Diagnosis: CT pulmonary angiography. Treatment: anticoagulation (Heparin, Rivaroxaban).", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира coronary artery disease?", "output": "CAD diagnosis: stress test, coronary CT angiography, cardiac catheterization. Symptoms: angina. Risk stratification guides invasive testing. PCI/stenting available in Bulgarian cardiac centers — НЗОК covered.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е hypertensive crisis?", "output": "Hypertensive crisis: BP > 180/120 with organ damage. Симптоми: severe headache, vision changes, chest pain. EMERGENCY treatment with IV antihypertensives in hospital. Gradual BP reduction — not too fast.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на endocarditis?", "output": "Endocarditis: fever, new heart murmur, embolic phenomena. Risk: valve disease, IV drug use. Diagnosis: blood cultures, echocardiography. Treatment: prolonged IV antibiotics. Infectious disease + cardiolog management.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува stable angina?", "output": "Stable angina: medical therapy first line. Medications: Beta-blockers, Calcium channel blockers, Nitrates, Ranolazine. НЗОК покрива Bisoprolol, Amlodipine, Isosorbide. Revascularization при refractory symptoms.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Wolff-Parkinson-White syndrome?", "output": "WPW е pre-excitation syndrome с palpitations, tachycardia. Diagnosis: ECG with delta wave. Treatment: catheter ablation — available in Sofia cardiac electrophysiology units. Beta-blockers for symptom control.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на aortic stenosis?", "output": "Aortic stenosis: dyspnea, angina, syncope (classic triad). Diagnosis: echocardiography. Severe: aortic valve replacement. TAVI available in Bulgaria for high-risk patients.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява post-MI recovery?", "output": "Post-MI: cardiac rehabilitation, dual antiplatelet therapy (Aspirin + Clopidogrel), statins, ACE inhibitors, Beta-blockers. НЗОК covers all. Lifestyle modification critical. Cardiolog follow-up at 1, 3, 6 months.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е vasovagal syncope?", "output": "Vasovagal syncope е common fainting from trigger (pain, emotion). Usually benign. Diagnosis: history, tilt table test. Treatment: hydration, compression stockings, physical counterpressure maneuvers.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на heart failure with preserved EF?", "output": "HFpEF: dyspnea, edema with normal ejection fraction. Common in elderly, hypertensive, diabetic women. Treatment: diuretics, treat comorbidities. SGLT2 inhibitors increasingly used — частично покрити.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира long QT syndrome?", "output": "Long QT: prolonged QT interval on ECG, syncope, sudden death risk. Diagnosis: ECG, genetic testing. Treatment: Beta-blockers, ICD for high risk. Avoid QT-prolonging medications.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е peripheral artery disease?", "output": "PAD: leg pain with walking (claudication), reduced pulses. Risk: smoking, diabetes. Diagnosis: ankle-brachial index. Treatment: exercise, statins, antiplatelets, revascularization. Smoking cessation essential.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на myocarditis?", "output": "Myocarditis: chest pain, dyspnea, palpitations post-viral illness. Diagnosis: troponin, MRI, biopsy. Treatment: rest, heart failure meds, avoid sports 3-6 months. Cardiolog monitoring.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува bradycardia?", "output": "Symptomatic bradycardia may need pacemaker. Causes: sick sinus syndrome, AV block. Diagnosis: Holter monitoring. Pacemaker implantation — НЗОК covered in approved centers.", "category": "Кардиология"},
    # ── Неврология (Neurology) ──
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на multiple sclerosis?", "output": "MS причинява vision problems, numbness, weakness, fatigue, balance issues. В България ~4000 patients. Diagnosis: MRI, CSF oligoclonal bands. Treatment: Interferon beta, Dimethyl fumarate — покрити от НЗОК. Neurolog referral.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е ischemic stroke?", "output": "Ischemic stroke е blocked brain artery. Symptoms: FAST — Face drooping, Arm weakness, Speech difficulty, Time to call 112. Treatment: thrombolysis within 4.5h, thrombectomy. Bulgarian stroke units in major cities.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува epilepsy?", "output": "Epilepsy: recurrent seizures. Diagnosis: EEG, MRI. Treatment: Valproate, Levetiracetam (Keppra), Lamotrigine — покрити от НЗОК. Avoid triggers, medication compliance. Neurolog follow-up.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на migraine?", "output": "Migraine: throbbing headache, nausea, photophobia, aura possible. Triggers: stress, hormones, foods. Treatment: Sumatriptan (Imigran), Prophylaxis: Propranolol, Topiramate — покрити от НЗОК.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Parkinson disease?", "output": "Parkinson: tremor, bradykinesia, rigidity, postural instability. Diagnosis: clinical. Treatment: Levodopa/Carbidopa (Sinemet), Pramipexole — покрити от НЗОК. Physiotherapy, occupational therapy.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на Alzheimer disease?", "output": "Alzheimer: memory loss, confusion, personality changes. Diagnosis: cognitive testing, MRI. Treatment: Donepezil (Aricept), Memantine — покрити от НЗОК. Caregiver support, safety modifications.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира peripheral neuropathy?", "output": "Neuropathy: numbness, tingling, burning in feet/hands. Causes: diabetes most common. Diagnosis: nerve conduction studies. Treatment: Gabapentin (Neurontin), Pregabalin — покрити от НЗОК. Control underlying cause.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е trigeminal neuralgia?", "output": "Trigeminal neuralgia: severe facial pain episodes. Triggered by touch, chewing. Treatment: Carbamazepine (Tegretol) first line — покрит от НЗОК. Surgical options if refractory.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на meningitis?", "output": "Meningitis: headache, fever, neck stiffness, altered consciousness. EMERGENCY — 112. Bacterial meningitis needs immediate IV antibiotics. Vaccination prevention available.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува cluster headache?", "output": "Cluster headache: severe unilateral orbital pain, autonomic symptoms. Treatment: Sumatriptan, Oxygen therapy, Verapamil prophylaxis. Neurolog referral. Avoid alcohol during cluster period.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Guillain-Barré syndrome?", "output": "GBS: ascending paralysis post-infection. EMERGENCY — hospitalization. Treatment: IV immunoglobulin, plasmapheresis. Most recover but may need ventilation. Neurolog + ICU care.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на Bell palsy?", "output": "Bell palsy: sudden facial weakness one side. Diagnosis: clinical, exclude stroke. Treatment: Prednisolone within 72h — покрит от НЗОК. Eye protection. Most recover in 3-6 months.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява chronic migraine?", "output": "Chronic migraine: ≥15 headache days/month. Prophylaxis: Topiramate, Amitriptyline, Botox — частично покрити. Lifestyle: sleep hygiene, stress management. Headache diary.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е restless legs syndrome?", "output": "RLS: urge to move legs, worse at night. Associated with iron deficiency. Treatment: Iron replacement if deficient, Pramipexole, Gabapentin. Sleep hygiene important.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на brain tumor?", "output": "Brain tumor: headache, seizures, focal neurological deficits, personality change. Diagnosis: MRI with contrast. Treatment: surgery, radiation, chemotherapy per type. Referral to neuro-oncology center.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува tension headache?", "output": "Tension headache: bilateral pressing pain, stress-related. Treatment: Paracetamol, Ibuprofen, stress management, physiotherapy. Avoid medication overuse. Regular exercise helps prevention.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е transverse myelitis?", "output": "Transverse myelitis: spinal cord inflammation causing weakness, sensory loss. Diagnosis: MRI spine. Treatment: high-dose steroids, plasmapheresis. Neurolog rehabilitation.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на myasthenia gravis?", "output": "Myasthenia gravis: fatigable muscle weakness, ptosis, dysphagia. Diagnosis: acetylcholine receptor antibodies. Treatment: Pyridostigmine, Prednisolone, Thymectomy. Neurolog management.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира carpal tunnel syndrome?", "output": "CTS: numbness in thumb, index, middle fingers, worse at night. Diagnosis: nerve conduction study. Treatment: wrist splint, steroid injection, surgery. Occupational factors common.", "category": "Неврология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е hemorrhagic stroke?", "output": "Hemorrhagic stroke: bleeding in brain. Symptoms: sudden severe headache, vomiting, decreased consciousness. EMERGENCY — 112. Risk: hypertension, anticoagulation. Neurosurgical intervention may be needed.", "category": "Неврология"},
    # ── Онкология (Oncology) ──
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на lung cancer?", "output": "Lung cancer: persistent cough, hemoptysis, chest pain, weight loss. Most common cancer in Bulgarian men. Diagnosis: chest CT, biopsy. Treatment: surgery, chemotherapy, immunotherapy. Smoking cessation critical.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е colorectal cancer screening?", "output": "Colorectal cancer: second most common in Bulgaria. Screening: colonoscopy age 50-75, FIT test. Symptoms: rectal bleeding, change in bowel habits. Treatment: surgery, chemotherapy. НЗОК covers screening for eligible.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на breast cancer?", "output": "Breast cancer: lump, nipple changes, skin dimpling. Screening: mammography age 50-69 every 2 years — НЗОК program. Treatment: surgery, radiation, hormone therapy, chemotherapy per stage.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува prostate cancer?", "output": "Prostate cancer: often asymptomatic early. Screening: PSA, DRE discussion age 50+. Treatment: active surveillance, surgery, radiation, hormone therapy. Oncolog referral in approved centers.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е chemotherapy side effects management?", "output": "Chemo side effects: nausea (Ondansetron — покрит), fatigue, hair loss, neutropenia. Supportive care: G-CSF for neutropenia, antiemetics. Oncolog coordinates. Nutritional support important.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на lymphoma?", "output": "Lymphoma: lymph node swelling, B symptoms (fever, night sweats, weight loss). Diagnosis: biopsy, PET-CT. Treatment: chemotherapy, immunotherapy (Rituximab). Hematology-oncology referral.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира melanoma?", "output": "Melanoma: ABCDE criteria for moles — Asymmetry, Border, Color, Diameter, Evolution. Diagnosis: excision biopsy. Treatment: wide excision, sentinel node, immunotherapy for advanced. Dermatolog screening.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е palliative care?", "output": "Palliative care: symptom management, quality of life for serious illness. Available in Bulgarian hospices and hospitals. Pain management: Morphine — покрит от НЗОК. Psychosocial support for patient and family.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са risk factors за cancer в България?", "output": "Risk factors: smoking (40% lung cancer), alcohol, obesity, HPV (cervical), HBV/HCV (liver). Prevention: vaccination, screening programs, lifestyle. Bulgarian National Cancer Plan promotes early detection.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува cervical cancer?", "output": "Cervical cancer prevention: HPV vaccination (in Bulgarian calendar), Pap smear screening. Treatment: surgery, radiation, chemotherapy by stage. НЗОК covers HPV vaccine for girls age 12.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е immunotherapy in cancer?", "output": "Immunotherapy: checkpoint inhibitors (Pembrolizumab, Nivolumab) for various cancers. Partially covered by НЗОК for approved indications. Oncolog determines eligibility. Side effects: immune-related adverse events.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на pancreatic cancer?", "output": "Pancreatic cancer: jaundice, abdominal pain, weight loss, new-onset diabetes. Poor prognosis. Diagnosis: CT, CA 19-9. Treatment: surgery if resectable, chemotherapy. Early detection difficult.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява cancer pain?", "output": "Cancer pain: WHO analgesic ladder. Step 1: Paracetamol/NSAIDs. Step 2: weak opioids. Step 3: Morphine, Fentanyl — покрити от НЗОК. Palliative care team support.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е leukemia?", "output": "Leukemia: blood cancer with fatigue, infections, bleeding. Types: ALL, AML, CLL, CML. Diagnosis: blood count, bone marrow biopsy. Treatment: chemotherapy, targeted therapy, transplant. Hematology referral.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на bladder cancer?", "output": "Bladder cancer: hematuria most common symptom. Risk: smoking. Diagnosis: cystoscopy, CT urogram. Treatment: TURBT, intravesical therapy, cystectomy for invasive. Urolog + oncolog care.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира thyroid cancer?", "output": "Thyroid cancer: neck lump, often incidental on ultrasound. Diagnosis: FNA biopsy. Treatment: thyroidectomy, radioiodine for differentiated types. Prognosis generally good. Endocrinolog + surgeon.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е cancer survivorship care?", "output": "Survivorship: follow-up for recurrence, manage late effects, psychosocial support. Bulgarian cancer survivors need long-term oncolog follow-up. Lifestyle: exercise, healthy diet, screening for second cancers.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на ovarian cancer?", "output": "Ovarian cancer: bloating, pelvic pain, early satiety — often late presentation. Diagnosis: CA-125, ultrasound, surgery. Treatment: debulking surgery, chemotherapy. Genetic testing for BRCA.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува stomach cancer?", "output": "Stomach cancer: epigastric pain, weight loss, anemia. Risk: H. pylori, smoking. Diagnosis: gastroscopy with biopsy. Treatment: gastrectomy, chemotherapy. H. pylori eradication prevents.", "category": "Онкология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е radiation therapy?", "output": "Radiation therapy uses ionizing radiation to kill cancer cells. Available in Sofia, Plovdiv, Varna cancer centers — НЗОК covered. Side effects depend on site. Oncolog + radiation oncolog plan treatment.", "category": "Онкология"},
    # ── НЗОК и здравна система ──
    {"instruction": "Как работи системата на направления в България?", "output": "Направления (referrals) от личен лекар към специалист са задължителни за НЗОК покритие. Valid 30 days. Електронни направления чрез NHIS система. Без направление — плащате пълната цена.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какво покрива НЗОК за лекарства?", "output": "НЗОК Positive Drug List покрива ~800 лекарства с copayment 0-100%. Пълно покритие за chronic diseases (диабет, CVD, oncology). Рецепта от лекар, valid 30 days. E-prescription mandatory.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как се издава болничен лист?", "output": "Болничен (sick leave) се издава от личен лекар или специалист до 14 days, после medical commission. НЗОК pays 80% от average salary from day 4. Electronic sick leave since 2021.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е личен лекар и как да се запиша?", "output": "Личен лекар (GP) е mandatory за НЗОК. Registration at chosen practice with ID and health insurance card. Can change GP twice yearly. GP coordinates all care and referrals.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какви прегledи покрива НЗОК?", "output": "НЗОК covers: GP visits, specialist with referral, preventive exams (mammography, colonoscopy age-eligible), vaccinations in calendar, emergency care. Dental: limited coverage for children.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как работи електронната здравна карта?", "output": "Electronic Health Record (EHR) in NHIS contains prescriptions, referrals, diagnoses. Doctors access with patient consent. Patients can view via patient portal. Mandatory for all healthcare providers.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е допълнително здравно осигуряване?", "output": "ДЗО (voluntary health insurance) supplements НЗОК with faster access, private rooms, dental. Major providers: ДЗИ, Булстрад, Уника. Not mandatory but popular for specialist access.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как се получава медицинска помощ в спешност?", "output": "Emergency care (112 or direct to ER) is free for all regardless of insurance. ER triage system. After stabilization, НЗОК covers if insured. University hospitals in Sofia, Plovdiv, Varna have 24h ER.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какви документи са нужни за НЗОК?", "output": "Required: Bulgarian health insurance card (ЗОК), ID card. EU citizens: EHIC card. Uninsured pay full cost. Registration at Regional Health Insurance Fund.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как работи хоспитализацията по НЗОК?", "output": "Hospital admission with referral or emergency. НЗОК covers hospital stay, procedures, medications during stay. Patient chooses from contracted hospitals. Copayment may apply for some services.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какво покрива НЗОК за бременни?", "output": "Pregnancy care fully covered: prenatal visits, ultrasounds, lab tests, delivery. High-risk pregnancy monitoring. Postnatal care for mother and newborn. Register pregnancy with GP early.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как се оспорва отказ за лекарство от НЗОК?", "output": "If medication not on Positive List, doctor can request individual approval (Индивидуално разрешение) with medical justification. Commission reviews within 14 days. Appeal to RHIF if denied.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е ТЕЛК и как работи?", "output": "TELK (medical commission for disability) assesses disability degree. Required for disability pension and benefits. Application through GP. Reassessment every 1-5 years depending on condition.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Какви вaccини покрива НЗОК?", "output": "НЗОК covers all mandatory vaccinations in national calendar: BCG, DTP, MMR, HPV, etc. Free at GP or school. Optional vaccines (flu, travel) may have partial coverage for risk groups.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    {"instruction": "Как работи домашното лечение?", "output": "Home care by GP or visiting nurse for bedridden patients. НЗОК covers home visits, some nursing care. Application through GP with medical justification. Available in all regions.", "category": "НЗОК и здравна система"},
    # ── Спешна медицина ──
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при сърдечен арест?", "output": "При cardiac arrest: call 112, start CPR (30 compressions : 2 breaths), use AED if available. Bulgarian EMS target response time < 8 min in cities. Continue CPR until EMS arrives.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да спра тежко кръvorazливane?", "output": "Direct pressure on wound with clean cloth. Elevate if possible. Tourniquet for limb bleeding if pressure fails. Call 112. Do not remove embedded objects. Bulgarian first aid courses available through Red Cross.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при алергичен shock?", "output": "Anaphylaxis: call 112, administer Epinephrine (EpiPen) if available, lay flat with legs elevated. Common triggers: food, insect stings, medications. Second dose in 5-15 min if needed.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да помогна при инсулт?", "output": "FAST assessment: Face, Arms, Speech, Time. Call 112 immediately. Note time of symptom onset. Do not give food/water. Stroke units: Sofia (Pirogov), Plovdiv, Varna, Burgas.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при изгаряне?", "output": "Cool burn with running water 20 min. Cover with clean dressing. Do not apply butter/ice. Call 112 for severe burns (> palm size, face, genitals). Bulgarian burn center at Pirogov Hospital Sofia.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да реагирам при отравяне?", "output": "Call 112 and Poison Control Center Sofia: +359 2 9154 123. Do not induce vomiting unless instructed. Bring container/substance info. Activated charcoal if advised. Common: medications, household chemicals.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при epileptic seizure?", "output": "Protect from injury, do not restrain, do not put anything in mouth. Time the seizure. Call 112 if > 5 min or first seizure. Recovery position after seizure ends. Stay with person.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да помогна при задушаване?", "output": "Conscious: back blows and abdominal thrusts (Heimlich). Unconscious: start CPR. Call 112. For infants: back blows and chest thrusts. Bulgarian Red Cross offers first aid training.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при hypoglycemia?", "output": "If conscious: give 15g fast-acting sugar (juice, glucose tablets). Recheck in 15 min. If unconscious: call 112, recovery position, do not give oral glucose. Glucagon injection if available.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да реагирам при snake bite?", "output": "Keep calm, immobilize limb, call 112. Do not cut wound or suck venom. Note snake appearance if safe. Antivenom available at major hospitals. Bulgaria has few venomous snakes ( horned viper).", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при heat stroke?", "output": "Move to cool place, remove excess clothing, cool with water/fan. Call 112. Heat stroke is EMERGENCY — confusion, hot dry skin, temperature > 40°C. IV fluids in hospital. Common in Bulgarian summer.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да помогна при panic attack?", "output": "Stay calm, guide slow breathing (4-7-8 technique), move to quiet space. Reassure it will pass. If chest pain or first episode — call 112 to rule out cardiac cause. Follow up with psychiatrist.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при fracture?", "output": "Immobilize limb, apply ice, elevate if possible. Do not try to realign. Call 112 for open fractures. Splint in position found. Bulgarian ER has orthopedic coverage 24/7.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Как да реагирам при drowning?", "output": "Remove from water safely, call 112. If not breathing: start CPR. Even if recovered, hospital evaluation needed (dry drowning risk). Bulgarian Black Sea lifeguard stations in summer.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво да правя при drug overdose?", "output": "Call 112 immediately. Naloxone (Narcan) for opioid overdose if available. Do not leave person alone. Bring medication containers. Bulgarian toxicology at Pirogov Hospital.", "category": "Спешна медицина"},
    # ── Лекарства и фармакология ──
    {"instruction": "Какво е Алфа Норм и за какво се използва?", "output": "Алфа Норм (Metformin) е oral antidiabetic first-line за тип 2 диабет. НЗОК покрит напълно. Dose: start 500mg 1-2x daily with meals, titrate to 2000mg. Side effects: GI upset, rare lactic acidosis.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са страничните ефекти на Enalapril?", "output": "Enalapril (ACE inhibitor): dry cough (10%), hyperkalemia, angioedema (rare). НЗОК покрит. Monitor kidney function and potassium. Contraindicated in pregnancy. Take in morning.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е взаимодействието между Warfarin и Aspirin?", "output": "Warfarin + Aspirin significantly increases bleeding risk. Avoid combination unless specifically prescribed (e.g., post-stent). Monitor INR closely. Alternative: use single antiplatelet or NOAC.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се приема Omeprazole?", "output": "Omeprazole (PPI): 20-40mg once daily before breakfast, 30 min before food. НЗОК покрит. Duration: max 8 weeks for GERD without investigation. Long-term: monitor B12, magnesium.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Atorvastatin и кога се prescribes?", "output": "Atorvastatin (statin): lowers LDL cholesterol. НЗОК покрит. Dose: 10-80mg daily. Target LDL per risk category. Side effects: muscle pain (check CK), liver enzymes. Take in evening.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са дозировките на Amoxicillin?", "output": "Amoxicillin: 500mg 3x daily for 7 days (respiratory infections), 875mg 2x daily (sinusitis). НЗОК покрит. Complete full course. Allergy: check for penicillin allergy. Adjust in renal impairment.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Levothyroxine dosing?", "output": "Levothyroxine (Euthyrox): take on empty stomach, 30-60 min before breakfast. Start 25-50mcg, titrate by TSH every 6-8 weeks. НЗОК покрит. Do not switch brands without monitoring.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са interactions на Ciprofloxacin?", "output": "Ciprofloxacin interactions: antacids (reduce absorption — separate 2h), Warfarin (increased INR), theophylline. Avoid dairy within 2h. Tendon rupture risk — avoid in elderly on steroids.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Paracetamol maximum dose?", "output": "Paracetamol (Efferalgan, Panadol): max 4g/day adults, 60mg/kg children. НЗОК покрит OTC. Hepatotoxic in overdose. Safe in pregnancy. Avoid alcohol. Check combination products for hidden paracetamol.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се приема Metformin правилно?", "output": "Metformin: with meals to reduce GI side effects. Start low, increase gradually. Hold before contrast CT and surgery. Monitor B12 annually. НЗОК first-line for T2DM.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Bisoprolol и за какво?", "output": "Bisoprolol (beta-blocker): hypertension, heart failure, angina. Start 2.5-5mg daily. НЗОК покрит. Do not stop abruptly. Contraindicated in asthma. Monitor heart rate.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са страничните ефекти на Metformin?", "output": "Metformin side effects: nausea, diarrhea (usually transient), B12 deficiency (long-term), rare lactic acidosis. Take with food. Contraindicated if eGFR < 30. Most common first-line antidiabetic in Bulgaria.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Clopidogrel?", "output": "Clopidogrel (Plavix): antiplatelet for post-MI, stroke, stent. 75mg daily. НЗОК покрит. Combined with Aspirin for 12 months post-stent. PPI interaction (avoid Omeprazole — use Pantoprazole).", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се приема Salbutamol inhaler?", "output": "Salbutamol (Ventolin): 1-2 puffs as needed for asthma/COPD. Max 8 puffs/day. НЗОК покрит. Shake before use. Rinse mouth after. If using > 2 days/week, need controller medication.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Sertraline dosing?", "output": "Sertraline (Zoloft): start 50mg daily for depression/anxiety. Titrate to 100-200mg. НЗОК покрит. Takes 4-6 weeks for full effect. Do not stop abruptly. Avoid with MAOIs.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са generic vs brand в България?", "output": "Bulgarian pharmacies must offer cheapest generic unless doctor writes 'DA' (dispense as written). Generic equivalence verified by BDA. Significant cost savings with generics. НЗОК prefers generics.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Insulin dosing basics?", "output": "Insulin types in Bulgaria: rapid (NovoRapid), long (Lantus/Tresiba). НЗОК покрит for T1DM and T2DM on insulin. Basal-bolus regimen standard. Storage: refrigerate, room temp 28 days.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са interactions на Ibuprofen?", "output": "Ibuprofen: avoid with Warfarin (bleeding), ACE inhibitors (reduced effect), other NSAIDs. GI risk — use with food. Max 1200mg/day OTC. НЗОК покрит. Avoid in renal impairment.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е Amlodipine?", "output": "Amlodipine (calcium channel blocker): hypertension, angina. 5-10mg daily. НЗОК покрит. Side effects: ankle edema, flushing. Long half-life — once daily dosing.", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    {"instruction": "Как се съхраняват лекарства правилно?", "output": "Store per label: most at room temp (< 25°C), some refrigerated. Keep in original packaging. Check expiry. Bulgarian pharmacies provide storage advice. Do not store in bathroom (humidity).", "category": "Лекарства и фармакология"},
    # ── Педиатрия ──
    {"instruction": "Какъв е вaccinaционният календар в България?", "output": "Bulgarian immunization calendar: BCG (birth), HepB (birth, 2, 6mo), DTP (2, 4, 6mo), Hib, PCV, MMR (12mo), varicella (12mo), HPV girls (12yr). Free through НЗОК at GP.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на roseola при деца?", "output": "Roseola (HHV-6): high fever 3-5 days then rash when fever breaks. Age 6mo-2yr. Self-limited. Treatment: antipyretics (Paracetamol), fluids. Rare febrile seizures — call doctor if seizure.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува otitis media при деца?", "output": "Acute otitis media: ear pain, fever. Watchful waiting for > 2yr with mild symptoms. Amoxicillin first line if treating. НЗОК покрит. Follow-up if not improving in 48-72h.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е bronchiolitis при бебета?", "output": "Bronchiolitis (RSV): wheezing, cough in infants < 1yr. Supportive care: suction, hydration. No routine bronchodilators/antibiotics. Hospital if respiratory distress. Peak winter in Bulgaria.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на ADHD?", "output": "ADHD: inattention, hyperactivity, impulsivity affecting function. Diagnosis: clinical, age > 6. Treatment: Methylphenidate (Concerta), behavioral therapy. НЗОК partial coverage. Pediatric psychiatrist.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява childhood asthma?", "output": "Pediatric asthma: inhaled corticosteroids (Fluticasone), SABA for rescue. Asthma action plan. Trigger avoidance. НЗОК covers medications. Pediatric pneumolog follow-up.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е febrile seizure?", "output": "Febrile seizures: 2-5% of children age 6mo-5yr with fever. Usually benign. Call 112 if > 5 min. After first: pediatric evaluation. Antipyretics for comfort, not proven to prevent recurrence.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на chickenpox?", "output": "Varicella: itchy vesicular rash, fever. Vaccine in calendar at 12mo. Treatment: supportive, antihistamines, avoid scratching. Complications rare. Keep home until crusted. Calamine lotion.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Как се диагностицира developmental delay?", "output": "Developmental screening at well-child visits. Milestones: walking 12mo, words 12mo, sentences 2yr. Early intervention critical. Bulgarian social-pediatric services available. GP referral to specialist.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е colic при бебета?", "output": "Infant colic: crying > 3h/day, > 3 days/week, < 3mo. Rule out organic causes. Strategies: swaddling, white noise, probiotic (Lactobacillus). Self-resolves by 3-4 months. Parent support important.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на croup?", "output": "Croup: barking cough, stridor, hoarseness. Viral, age 6mo-3yr. Mild: humidified air, steroids (Dexamethasone). Severe stridor: ER. НЗОК covers treatment. Peak autumn/winter.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува impetigo при деца?", "output": "Impetigo: bacterial skin infection, honey-crusted lesions. Treatment: topical Mupirocin (mild) or oral Flucloxacillin (widespread). НЗОК покрит. Keep child home until 24h antibiotics. Good hygiene.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е growth monitoring?", "output": "Growth charts at every well-child visit. Height, weight, BMI, head circumference. Bulgarian pediatric growth standards used. Failure to thrive needs investigation. НЗОК covers all visits.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на hand-foot-mouth?", "output": "HFMD: vesicles on hands, feet, mouth, fever. Viral, self-limited. Treatment: supportive, soft foods, fluids. Contagious — keep home. Peak summer. Rare complications: meningitis.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    {"instruction": "Как се управлява childhood obesity?", "output": "Pediatric obesity: BMI > 95th percentile. Family-based lifestyle intervention. Limit screen time, increase activity, healthy diet. НЗОК covers dietitian referral. Avoid weight loss drugs in children.", "category": "Педиатрия"},
    # ── Психично здраве ──
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на depression?", "output": "Depression: persistent sadness, anhedonia, sleep/appetite changes, fatigue, guilt, concentration problems > 2 weeks. Treatment: Sertraline, Escitalopram — НЗОК покрити. Psychotherapy (CBT). Crisis line: 0800 1 8040.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е generalized anxiety disorder?", "output": "GAD: excessive worry > 6 months, restlessness, fatigue, muscle tension. Treatment: SSRIs (Escitalopram), CBT. НЗОК covers medication and partial psychotherapy. Psychiatrist referral.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува panic disorder?", "output": "Panic disorder: recurrent panic attacks with fear of recurrence. Treatment: SSRIs, CBT, breathing techniques. Avoid benzodiazepines long-term. НЗОК covers Sertraline. Psychiatrist management.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е burnout и как да го разпозная?", "output": "Burnout: emotional exhaustion, depersonalization, reduced accomplishment from chronic work stress. Common in Bulgarian healthcare workers. Management: boundaries, rest, therapy, sometimes medication. Not a clinical diagnosis but real syndrome.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на PTSD?", "output": "PTSD: re-experiencing, avoidance, hyperarousal after trauma. Treatment: trauma-focused CBT, EMDR, SSRIs (Sertraline). НЗОК partial coverage. Bulgarian veterans and trauma survivors need specialized care.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува insomnia?", "output": "Insomnia: CBT-I first line (sleep hygiene, stimulus control). Medications short-term: Zolpidem, Melatonin. Avoid long-term benzodiazepines. Address underlying depression/anxiety.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е bipolar disorder?", "output": "Bipolar: alternating depression and mania/hypomania. Treatment: mood stabilizers (Lithium, Valproate), atypical antipsychotics. НЗОК covers Lithium with monitoring. Psychiatrist essential.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на OCD?", "output": "OCD: obsessions (intrusive thoughts) and compulsions (rituals). Treatment: SSRIs (high dose Fluoxetine), ERP therapy. НЗОК covers medication. Psychologist for CBT/ERP.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Как да помогна на близък с suicidal thoughts?", "output": "Take seriously, ask directly about suicide, stay with person, remove means, call 112 or crisis line 0800 1 8040. Do not leave alone. Emergency psychiatric evaluation. Bulgarian crisis services available 24/7.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е social anxiety disorder?", "output": "Social anxiety: fear of social situations, performance anxiety. Treatment: CBT, SSRIs (Paroxetine, Sertraline). НЗОК covers medication. Gradual exposure therapy effective.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Как се лекува ADHD при възрастни?", "output": "Adult ADHD: inattention, impulsivity from childhood. Diagnosis: clinical history. Treatment: Methylphenidate, Atomoxetine. НЗОК partial coverage. Psychiatrist diagnosis required.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е eating disorder?", "output": "Eating disorders (anorexia, bulimia): distorted body image, restrictive/binge-purge behavior. Treatment: nutritional rehabilitation, CBT, SSRIs for bulimia. Multidisciplinary team. Early intervention critical.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на schizophrenia?", "output": "Schizophrenia: hallucinations, delusions, disorganized thinking. Onset late teens/early 20s. Treatment: antipsychotics (Risperidone, Olanzapine) — НЗОК покрити. Long-term psychiatrist care. Community support.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Как да управлявам stress?", "output": "Stress management: regular exercise, sleep hygiene, mindfulness, social support, time management. If persistent: CBT, SSRIs. Bulgarian workplace mental health improving but stigma remains. GP can refer.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е seasonal affective disorder?", "output": "SAD: depression linked to reduced daylight in winter. Common in Bulgaria Nov-March. Treatment: light therapy (10,000 lux, 30 min morning), SSRIs, vitamin D. Exercise outdoors when possible.", "category": "Психично здраве"},
    # ── Профилактика ──
    {"instruction": "Какви скрining програми има в България?", "output": "Bulgarian screening: mammography (women 50-69, biennial), cervical cytology (25-65), colorectal FIT (50-74), newborn screening, cardiovascular risk assessment. НЗОК covers all eligible.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя CVD?", "output": "CVD prevention: no smoking, Mediterranean diet, 150 min exercise/week, BP < 140/90, LDL control, diabetes management. Bulgarian diet rich in vegetables, olive oil. Regular GP checkups.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е healthy diet за българи?", "output": "Bulgarian healthy diet: seasonal vegetables, yogurt (kiselo mlyako), legumes, whole grains, moderate meat, olive/sunflower oil. Limit: processed meats, sugary drinks, excessive rakia/wine. Traditional diet is naturally Mediterranean.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какви вaccini препоръчват за пътуване?", "output": "Travel vaccines: HepA, Typhoid (exotic travel), Tick-borne encephalitis (forests), Rabies (remote areas). Available at travel clinics Sofia. Not all НЗОК covered — check before travel.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя diabetes?", "output": "Diabetes prevention: maintain healthy weight, 150 min exercise/week, whole grains over refined, limit sugary drinks. Bulgarian diabetes prevalence rising — screening from age 45. Pre-diabetes reversible with lifestyle.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е sun protection в България?", "output": "Bulgarian summer UV index high (8-10). Use SPF 30+, reapply every 2h, avoid 11-16h sun. Skin cancer screening for new/changing moles. Black Sea tourists especially at risk.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя osteoporosis?", "output": "Osteoporosis prevention: calcium 1000mg/day, vitamin D 800-1000 IU, weight-bearing exercise, no smoking, limit alcohol. Bulgarian women post-menopause high risk. DEXA screening age 65.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е smoking cessation support?", "output": "Bulgaria has high smoking rates (35%). Quit support: Varenicline (Champix) — НЗОК покрит, nicotine replacement, counseling. Benefits begin within 20 min of quitting. GP can prescribe.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какви прегledи да правя ежегодно?", "output": "Annual checkup: BP, BMI, fasting glucose, lipid panel, complete blood count. Age 50+: colon screening, mammography (women), prostate discussion (men). GP coordinates. НЗОК covers preventive visits.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя flu?", "output": "Flu prevention: annual vaccination (October-November), hand hygiene, avoid sick contacts. НЗОК free for 65+, chronic disease, healthcare workers. Bulgarian flu season Dec-Feb.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е physical activity recommendation?", "output": "WHO recommendation: 150 min moderate or 75 min vigorous exercise/week plus 2x strength training. Bulgarians can use mountains (Vitoshа, Rila) for hiking. Walking in cities counts. Start gradually.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя tick-borne diseases?", "output": "Tick prevention: repellents, long clothing in forests, check body after outdoor activities. TBE vaccination available for forest workers. Lyme disease: early antibiotic treatment. Peak: April-September.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е alcohol moderation?", "output": "Safe limits: ≤ 2 drinks/day men, ≤ 1 women. Bulgarian rakia culture — be aware of high alcohol content. Regular excess increases CVD, liver disease, cancer risk. AUDIT screening at GP.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя workplace burnout?", "output": "Burnout prevention: work-life boundaries, regular breaks, exercise, social connections, adequate sleep. Bulgarian Labor Code mandates rest periods. Seek help early if exhausted, cynical, ineffective.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е dental prevention?", "output": "Dental care: brush 2x daily, floss, limit sugar. НЗОК covers children dental, limited adult coverage. Bulgarian dental tourism popular but prevention cheaper. Checkups every 6 months.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя STI?", "output": "STI prevention: condoms, vaccination (HPV, HepB), regular testing if at risk. Free HIV testing at SPIN centers in Bulgaria. HPV vaccine in calendar prevents cervical cancer.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е mental health prevention?", "output": "Mental health prevention: social connections, physical activity, sleep, stress management, limit alcohol. Bulgarian crisis line: 0800 1 8040. Early intervention for anxiety/depression prevents chronicity.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя childhood obesity?", "output": "Childhood obesity prevention: limit screen time < 2h/day, daily active play, family meals, no sugary drinks. Bulgarian school lunch programs improving. Model healthy behavior as parents.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е cardiovascular risk scoring?", "output": "SCORE2 chart estimates 10-year CVD risk. Used in Bulgarian GP practices. High risk (> 5%): intensive lifestyle + statin consideration. Factors: age, sex, smoking, BP, cholesterol.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да поддърjam зdravo стареене?", "output": "Healthy aging: stay active, social engagement, cognitive stimulation, balanced diet, regular medical checkups, fall prevention (home safety). Bulgarian pensioners eligible for free flu vaccine and preventive exams.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е hydration importance?", "output": "Adequate hydration: 1.5-2L water/day, more in Bulgarian hot summers. Dehydration causes confusion in elderly, kidney stones. Limit excessive coffee/alcohol. Monitor urine color.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя food poisoning?", "output": "Food safety: cook meat thoroughly, refrigerate promptly, separate raw/cooked, wash hands. Bulgarian summer BBQs — ensure meat cooked. Common pathogens: Salmonella, Campylobacter. Seek care if bloody diarrhea.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е sleep hygiene?", "output": "Sleep hygiene: consistent schedule, dark cool room, no screens 1h before bed, limit caffeine after 14h, exercise but not late. Bulgarian shift workers especially need attention. 7-9h for adults.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Как да предотвратя back pain?", "output": "Back pain prevention: core strengthening, proper lifting technique, ergonomic workspace, maintain healthy weight. Bulgarian office workers: stand breaks every hour. Physiotherapy available through НЗОК referral.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е cancer prevention lifestyle?", "output": "Cancer prevention: no smoking, limit alcohol, healthy weight, exercise, sun protection, vaccination (HPV, HepB), screening participation. 40% of cancers preventable. Bulgarian National Cancer Plan emphasizes prevention.", "category": "Профилактика"},
    {"instruction": "Какви са симптомите на грип при възрастни?", "output": "Грипът при възрастни се проявява с внезапна висока температура, мускулни болки, главоболие и суха кашлица. В България сезонът е от декември до февруари. НЗОК покрива противогрипна вaccina за рискови групи. Лечение: покой, течности, парацетамол.", "category": "Обща медицина"},
    {"instruction": "Какво е DEXA scan?", "output": "DEXA scan измерва костната плътност за диагностика на osteopenia и osteoporosis. Препоръчва се при жени след менопауза и мъже над 70 години с рискови фактори. НЗОК покрива прегледа при показания. Извършва се в болници и специализирани центрове.", "category": "Профилактика"},
]

